title: JOSEPHINE, LAB WHITE SAPPHIRE AND EMERALD DROP EARRINGS
description:
SOLD AS A PAIR.
A marquis shaped drop crafted from trillion cut lab-grown white sapphires and emeralds hang from an ornate halo stud on our Josephine Drop Earrings.
Josephine is part of a limited winter collection run. This style will not return in 2023 once sold out.
